{"tid":1893413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯收148宗求助包括孕婦 李慧琼：會請求中央政府協助「特事特辦」解決滯留中國的港人訴求！","createTime":"2020-02-23T08:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T01:58:01.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6239f1e3b7cbc576c0a90299e0bbcfe62d17fe","tid":1893413,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b2997115b012ce1db96f81e43ed3dfa482d04b","tid":1893413,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"車厘車厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af8af2b5b46b404f42f84947a298b9ee6ac9d1f","tid":1893413,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"民建聯開設微信號協助滯留內地港人，至今收到148宗求助個案，當中湖北有76宗。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯表示，148宗個案中，涉及藥物求助個案有55宗，希望盡快返回香港的有68宗。主席李慧琼說，已分批將求助個案交予政制及內地事務局跟進，亦已聯絡中聯辦協助。她說，會繼續要求特區政府盡快及盡力安排滯留湖北的港人回港，並請求中央政府協助，特事特辦，解決當地港人的急切訴求。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員葛珮帆表示，收到4宗涉及孕婦的求助個案，有家庭表示現時因現金、物資短缺，無法進行產檢，以致孕婦情緒焦慮，希望可以盡快回港產檢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBxLpON.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBxLpON.gif&h=17394007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510279-20200223.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510279-20200223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=6439c2b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510279-20200223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d8389580\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510279-20200223.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0df65fa4aa95c3c614e0e9d20bd0980004f0c594","tid":1893413,"uid":392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"re